
Changes
=======


0.5.2 (*2014-10-11*)
-----------------------

- fix bower release file


0.5.1 (*2014-10-10*)
-----------------------

- hoe.append() works for numbers without explicit conversion


0.5.0 (*2014-10-07*)
-----------------------

- update to polymer-platorm 0.4.2
- removed hoe.UI
- changes API for hoe.Component creation/initialization


0.4.0 (*2014-07-30*)
-----------------------

* backward-incompatible, most part of the API completely changed!

- removed dependency on jQuery, hoe() returns a HTML Node
- added hoe.extend()
- hoe() signature change, secondnd argument must be attributes
- added html manipulation function html(), fragment(), append(), remove()
- `forEach()` replaced by `forArray()` and `forDict()`
- `map()` replaced by `mapArray()` and `mapDict()`


0.3.0 (*2014-06-23*)
-----------------------

- added hoe.Component
- added hoe.UI

0.2.0 (*2013-01-27*)
------------------------

- added hoe.partial
- added hoe.Type.map
- added hoe.Type.scope
- rename hoe.Type.on to hoe.Type.listen
- rename hoe.Type.trigger to hoe.Type.fire
